com.yantra.ycp.qualifier

Interface YCPQualifiedTagValidator


  • public interface YCPQualifiedTagValidator
    This interface provides methods to validate Qualified Tag for a combination of Application Code and Application Version and to get the support level for Qualifer which is invalid for the combination. This interface is used by the APIs getRuleDetails and getCommonCodeList to check the validity of the qualifiedTag.
